com.intel.fightclub.coach.mediator.callbacks

Interface WearableStateChangedListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractWorkoutStatsFragment.WearableStateListenerImpl, SimpleWearableStateChangedListener

    public interface WearableStateChangedListener
    Listener that allows you to listen to changes of wearable state. Unless you have good reason you should inherit your implementation of WearableStateChangedListener from SimpleWearableStateChangedListener.
    See Also:
    SimpleWearableStateChangedListener

      • onTemporaryDisconnectionLevelChanged

        void onTemporaryDisconnectionLevelChanged(@NonNull
                                          TemporaryDisconnectionLevel newTemporaryDisconnectionLevel)
        Called when connection between glasses and application is temporarily disconnected. It allows you to show some overlay informing user that app is temporarily disconnected but app doing its best to fix the issue.
